Class SalesVP

java.lang.Object
Lab5.SalesAgent
Lab5.SalesSupervisor
Lab5.SalesChief
Lab5.SalesVP
public class SalesVP extends SalesChief
This class shows a Sales Vice President with stocks held. Name, age, location, and department are inherited from SalesChief, which in turn inherits name, age, and location.
Author:
Nouraldin Hassan
